    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <a href="https://tally.so/r/aQ52Lv" target="_blank" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-500 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/30 hover:shadow-blue-600/50 hover:-translate-y-1">
        Start My Project
        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
      </a>
      
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all flex items-center justify-center">
        How it works
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">Empowering local businesses in</p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 opacity-60 grayscale">
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-400 text-xl">KL</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-400 text-xl">Selangor</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-400 text-xl">Penang</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-slate-400 text-xl">Johor</span>
